        <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>
      </li>

      <li id="data" class="box resume">
        <a href="/about/#touch"><span class="strap">Data Analyst</span> 
          <span class="label"><span>G</span>ive <span>D</span>ata a <span>M</span>eaning</span></a>
          <span class="fl">W</span>e get lot of data which could be used to improve the way we live in our 
          houses. If you love finding patterns, visualizing data, and you feel confortable moving 
          around lot of data, 
          <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>        
      </li>

      <li id="security" class="box resume">
        <a href="/about/#touch"><span class="strap">Security Engineer</span> 
        <span class="label"><span>E</span>xploit <span>A</span>ccesses</span></a>
        <span class="fl">P</span>eople is scared about home automation. You have the role to prove 
        that Lelylan is secure and that no one can do anything without a given access. If you are 
        paranoid about security, <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>
      </li>

      <li id="energy" class="box last resume">
        <a href="/about/#touch"><span class="strap">Energy Saver</span> 
        <span class="label"><span>B</span>uild <span>E</span>fficient <span>H</span>ouses</span></a>
        <span class="fl">I</span>magine a world where houses produce energy, where smart grids exchange 
        informations, where people cares about the energy they use. If you want to be one of the people 
        teaching this, <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
